column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, g.h_beta_flux,g.h_beta_flux_err,g.oiii_#_flux,g.oiii_#_flux_err,g.oiii_#_flux,g.oiii_#_flux_err,g.nii_#_flux,g.nii_#_flux_err,g.h_alpha_flux,g.h_alpha_flux_err,g.nii_#_flux,g.nii_#_flux_err,g.sii_#_flux,g.sii_#_flux_err,g.sii_#_flux,g.sii_#_flux_err, g.ariii7#_eqw,g.ariii7#_eqw_err,s.specobjid, s.z as redshift FROM PhotoTag p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecLine as g ON g.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE  s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.class = &&&
